---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Valori" description="A small collective of AI practitioners. We build tools, run experiments, and publish what we learn.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <header class="mb-10">
      <a href="/" class="font-mono text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-neon-cyan transition-colors mb-4 inline-block">&larr; home</a>
      <h1 class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-text-bright glow-cyan">Valori</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-text-primary leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg">
        We're a small group of AI practitioners. We build tools, run experiments,
        and publish what we learn. That's it.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neon-green mb-3">Why anonymous?</h2>
        <p>
          Because the work matters more than the people. AI discourse is drowning
          in personal brands and hot takes attached to headshots. We'd rather
          the experiments speak for themselves.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neon-cyan mb-3">Why "Valori"?</h2>
        <p>
          From the Latin, to be of worth. We're interested in AI that has
          genuine value, not AI that generates hype.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neon-purple mb-3">Why "Soft Cat"?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-text-bright">S</strong>mart
          <strong class="text-text-bright">O</strong>utputs
          <strong class="text-text-bright">F</strong>rom
          <strong class="text-text-bright">T</strong>rained
          <strong class="text-text-bright">C</strong>onversational
          <strong class="text-text-bright">A</strong>I
          <strong class="text-text-bright">T</strong>echnology.
          Also, cats are good. The internet agrees on this.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neon-amber mb-3">What we actually do</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-neon-green mt-0.5">&#9656;</span>
            <span>Build and test AI agents and micro-tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-neon-green mt-0.5">&#9656;</span>
            <span>Run models against real tasks (not benchmarks)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-neon-green mt-0.5">&#9656;</span>
            <span>Monitor the AI landscape and filter signal from noise</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-neon-green mt-0.5">&#9656;</span>
            <span>Maintain this site, mostly through automation</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface border border-surface-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-text-bright mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <a href="mailto:workshop@softcat.ai" class="font-mono text-sm text-neon-cyan hover:underline">workshop@softcat.ai</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
